query:
SELECT id, name, isActive, createdAt, updatedAt
FROM prioritization_criteria
WHERE name IN (
  SELECT name
  FROM prioritization_criteria
  GROUP BY name
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
)
ORDER BY name, createdAt;
